io.dropwizard.validation

Annotation Type SizeRange


  • @Documented
@Constraint(validatedBy={})
@Target(value={METHOD,FIELD,ANNOTATION_TYPE,CONSTRUCTOR,PARAMETER})
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@MinSize(value=0L)
@MaxSize(value=9223372036854775807L,
         unit=TERABYTES)
public @interface SizeRange
    The annotated element has to be in the appropriate range. Apply on Size instances.
